Package: PeakQualityR
Title: Non-parametric comparison of peak shapes using moments and Mahalonobis distance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joe", "Knotts", , "j.knotts703@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Treats LC trace data as a probability distribution by multiplying retention time * intensity and summing the results. This data is then used to calculate all 4 statistical moments (mean, variance, skewness, kurtosis).
